<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> rājarāja</hi> tevarkku yāṇṭu 8<g type="dash"/>Āvatu <hi rend="grantha">śaśi</hi> kulacāḷukki taniniṉṟuveṉṟa viranāraciṅkatevanāṉa yātavarāyaneṉ nāyanār tirukkāḷattiuṭaiyanāyanār tevatānam Āṟṟū
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rnāṭṭuk koṉpākkattilum tirukkāḷattipputtūrilum nelvāyililum nāṉ koṇṭu<unclear>varu</unclear>m naṉcenilattil patti loṉṟāl <unclear>va</unclear>ṉta pāṭikāval nilam kaṭamaiyum ponnāyamum nel
<lb n="3" break="no"/>lāyamum Uṭppaṭa nāyanār tirukkāḷattiuṭaiya nāyanārkku tevatānamākavum neṭuṅkaṇil pāṭikāval nilattil kaṭamaiyum poṉnāyamum nellāyamum tirumalaiaṭivārattu nāṉ cey<unclear>vi</unclear>k<unclear>ki</unclear>ṟa viran<unclear>ā</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>raciṅkatevaṉ tiru<supplied reason="omitted">na</supplied>ntavanattukku veṇṭuvanattukkum tirunaṉtavanañ ceykiṟa Āḷkaḷukku coṟṟukkum Ilakkaikkum Uṭalā<supplied reason="omitted">ka</supplied>vum viṭṭeṉ viranāraciṅkatevanāṉa yātavarāyaneṉ <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="danda">.</g></supplied> Ivai yātavarāyaṉ Eḻuttu <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="danda">.</g></supplied> Itu paṉ<unclear>mā</unclear><note n="252-1">The letters <hi rend="grantha">heśvara ra kṣai</hi> are lost.</note>
</p>

